text: Hello how are you
Hello. Fine, thanks. You?
I am doing well thank you! Are you thinking of donating?
Yes I am
That is great! First, can I ask why you would like to donate?
Seems like the right thing to do
That is great! How much would you like to donate to the charity now?
I would like to donate $2
That is amazing! Thank you so much for your donation!
Glad to help
Would you like to hear where your donation is going?
Yes I would
Your donation will go to help childhood cancer research. It will directly benefit pediatric research.
Wonderful. Great use of a donation.
Would you feel conflicted if animals were involved in the research?
As a cancer survivor, no I would not.
Glad to hear that! Also, glad to hear you were able to fight the good fight!
Thank you. It's an important cause for me.
Thank you so much for your donation!
No problem. Glad to help.
